('Ivana Baquero', 'Ivana Baquero Macías is a Spanish actress. At the age of 11, Baquero was chosen by director Guillermo del Toro to play the lead role of Ofelia in Pan''''s Labyrinth, for which she won critical acclaim and the Goya Award for Best New Actress.', '1994-06-11', 'Barcelona, Spain', 'ivana_baquero.png'),
('Sergi López', 'Sergi López i Ayats (born 22 December 1965) is a Spanish actor.', '1965-12-22', 'Barcelona, Cataluña, Spain', 'sergi_lópez.png'),
('Maribel Verdú', 'María Isabel Verdú Rollán (born 2 October 1970), better known as Maribel Verdú, is a Spanish actress. She is the recipient of numerous accolades throughout her career spanning nearly four decades, including two Goya Awards for Best Actress, an Ariel Award for Best Actress, the Gold Medal of the Academy of Cinematographic Arts and Sciences of Spain in 2008 and the National Cinematography Award in 2009.  Verdú made her acting debut at the age of thirteen in Captain Sánchez''''s Crime (1985). Some of her film credits include performances in Lovers (1991), Belle Époque (1992), Y tu mamá también (2001), Pan''''s Labyrinth (2006), The Blind Sunflowers (2008), Tetro (2009), Snow White (2012) and Raymond & Ray (2022). She also appeared as Nora Allen in the DC Extended Universe film The Flash, her second superhero film credit after Superlópez (2018).', '1970-10-02', 'Madrid, Spain', 'maribel_verdú.png'),
